Go Stepper
===========

Stepper package provides super simple steps handler and
formatter.

Installation
------------
Use the `goinstall` tool:

	$ goinstall github.com/nu7hatch/gostepper

... or install it manually:

	$ git clone git://github.com/nu7hatch/gostepper.git
	$ cd gostepper
	$ make install

Usage
-----

	package main
	
	import stepper "github.com/nu7hatch/gostepper"
	import "net"

	func main() {
	    var s stepper.Stepper
	    s.Step("Connecting to the server")
	    conn, err := net.Dial("tcp", "127.0.0.1:8080")
	    if err != {
	        s.Fail(err.Error(), true)
	    }
	    s.Ok()
	}

